Date: 2 April 2020 Location: The Country Club Johannesburg, Auckland Park Website The PGMs Industry Day has established itself as a highly influential platform representing the views of the industry’s major stakeholders and draws representatives from local and international mining companies, investors, government and users of PGMs. This 3rd edition will tackle topical and relevant issues such as: the outlook for platinum group metals globally; supply and demand factors affecting the market; investors’ current perspectives; future markets and applications; the role of PGMs in the hydrogen economy; and much more.